Honest note on provenance and accuracy
---------------------------------------
The content is authored and curated by Jonas Nephtali with the assistance of
large language models, then corrected by hand. It is a work in progress, not a
vetted textbook. Known limitations at time of writing: residual niqqud errors
in some lessons, and the live translator runs on Google Translate under the
hood, so it can produce literal calques on idiomatic phrases. Do not present it
to learners as authoritative without checking. Corrections contributed back are
welcome.
